# Optional: a Gemini API key for local dev. Get one at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# The app also lets each user paste their own key at runtime (stored in their browser only).
# NOTE: a VITE_ var is exposed to the browser bundle — fine for a personal/demo build.
# For production, proxy Gemini through a backend so the key never ships to the client.
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=
